---
// How It Works Section Component
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">How Our YouTube Comment Analyzer Works</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">Get detailed sentiment insights in just three simple steps</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">1</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Paste YouTube URL</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Simply copy any YouTube video link and paste it into our analyzer. We support all YouTube URL formats including standard watch URLs, shortened links, and embedded URLs. <a href="https://support.google.com/youtube/answer/9706180?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">Learn about YouTube comment policies</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">2</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">AI Analysis</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Our advanced AI (<a href="https://platform.openai.com/docs/guides/gpt" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">OpenAI GPT-4o</a>) analyzes up to 100 comments, understanding context, sarcasm, and emotional nuances. The process typically takes 1-2 minutes.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-600">3</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Get Insights</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Receive detailed sentiment breakdowns, percentage analysis, sample comments, and a comprehensive summary of audience reactions to the video. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sentiment_analysis" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">What is sentiment analysis?</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Advanced Features -->
    <div class="mt-16 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center">Advanced AI Technology</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Context Understanding</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Our AI understands cultural references, industry-specific language, and contextual nuances that simpler tools miss.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
