            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Instant Results</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Get comprehensive sentiment analysis in 1-2 minutes. Perfect for content optimization and detailed insights.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
